{#
  Contact form posts straight to a Google Form's formResponse endpoint, so
  submissions land in the linked Google Sheet with no backend. The form targets
  a hidden iframe so the page does not navigate away to Google's confirmation
  screen; we show our own thank-you instead.

  Entry IDs are mapped from the form's pre-filled link. Field order in the
  Google Form: Name, WhatsApp number, Email, Preferred way, What's this about?,
  Message.

  Dropdown/choice option VALUES must match the Google Form exactly, or that
  answer lands blank in the Sheet.
#}
{% set formAction = "https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScVGlLUHvSgII5k7CeEijb48vaqdK9OcHr0Awx6KKIiHDujog/formResponse" %}
{% set entryName = "entry.905975239" %}
{% set entryWhatsapp = "entry.1915353865" %}
{% set entryEmail = "entry.1535906353" %}
{% set entryPreferred = "entry.37075721" %}
{% set entryTopic = "entry.1696634751" %}
{% set entryMessage = "entry.902539677" %}

